Text: Thank You so much.. You are a God among men..lol Great upload!

I appreciate the gesture and thanks for the upload, but I should warn people that this isn't a very quality website.  The content mostly focuses on the human characters in this series rather than the series' premise itself, the writing is subpar, and the creators seem to have a weak grasp of what's truly "sexy".  Maybe alright for a quick fix, but definitely not worth paying for.
